div.h1: TLB Coherency: Why Page Table Modifications Require Flushing

div.p: The TLB is a cacheit doesn't auto-update when page tables change.

ul.li: Next access triggers page table walk

div.p: Frame: 0x00123000 Flags: P=0, W=0, U=0 JUST MODIFIED!
TLB says: Present, Writable PTE says: Not Present!
TLB miss Page table walk PTE: Not Present Page Fault! (expected)
Cost: ~24 cycles Scope: One page only
asm ; Flush all non-global mov eax, cr3 mov cr3, eax
